    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Driving Rogue </strong></i>plunges you into a <i>high-speed rogue-like</i> challenge where every race is a fight for survival and mastery. Navigate treacherous city streets, execute precise manoeuvres, and <strong>beat  high scores</strong> to reach the very top!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088700/extras/15d0d694893a72153ab4055500a7ca49.poster.avif?t=1772040096\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088700/extras/15d0d694893a72153ab4055500a7ca49.webm?t=1772040096\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088700/extras/15d0d694893a72153ab4055500a7ca49.mp4?t=1772040096\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Core Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Drive, slipstream, near miss, drift</strong>, and <i>upgrade</i> your car to dominate the roads. Master the art of precision driving to finish each level with both style and speed, unlocking potent upgrades, fresh challenges, and new vehicles. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088700/extras/a663c3910bb25d2959044e0548615b8c.poster.avif?t=1772040096\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088700/extras/a663c3910bb25d2959044e0548615b8c.webm?t=1772040096\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088700/extras/a663c3910bb25d2959044e0548615b8c.mp4?t=1772040096\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Roguelike System</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After each race, visit the <strong>shop</strong> to grab new mods or unlock special abilities. Every run is procedurally generated - no two races are ever the same. Build your strategy, modify your car, and push for the longest streak you can. How far will your build take you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088700/extras/e5a842c142612e7817a930001c0533c5.poster.avif?t=1772040096\" width=1170 height=512 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088700/extras/e5a842c142612e7817a930001c0533c5.webm?t=1772040096\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unlockables!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand your garage with a lineup of <strong>unique cars</strong> — each with its own handling and flair. Personalise your ride with striking vinyls and stand out on every road.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088700/extras/ec231478e0f2b5b35993574e213a3976.poster.avif?t=1772040096\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088700/extras/ec231478e0f2b5b35993574e213a3976.webm?t=1772040096\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Biomes!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ride through diverse biomes, from neon-lit cities at night to winding countryside roads filled with iconic vehicles and roadside hazards you’ll want to spot… and avoid. Each environment comes alive with a varied soundtrack that matches the game’s nocturnal, adrenaline-fueled vibe. There’s always something new to discover and a fresh challenge around every curve.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088700/extras/81423a2fa6193285b8e80bbc3a6ca041.poster.avif?t=1772040096\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088700/extras/81423a2fa6193285b8e80bbc3a6ca041.webm?t=1772040096\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088700/extras/81423a2fa6193285b8e80bbc3a6ca041.mp4?t=1772040096\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Never Ending Fun</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chase the perfect run across a neon-fueled world. Beat your high scores, unlock new cars, collect achievements, and refine your strategy with every attempt. With diverse, upbeat tracks and a stylish, glowing world, drifting has never felt this smooth or addictive.</p>",
